<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head') %></head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Live vulnerable labs · OWASP Top 10 & beyond</div>
    <h1>Break real vulnerabilities.<br><span class="gradient-text">Learn how to stop them.</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">ZeroDay Academy is a hands-on web security training range by <strong>ZeroDay Security Services</strong>. Every challenge is a small, real, deliberately vulnerable web app — exploit it in its own tab, capture the flag, and understand exactly what went wrong in the code.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <% if (currentUser) { %>
        <a href="/challenges" class="btn btn-primary">Go to challenges</a>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-ghost">View dashboard</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Create free account</a>
        <a href="/challenges" class="btn btn-ghost">Preview challenges</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="glass stat"><div class="num"><%= stats.challengeCount %></div><div class="label">Vulnerability labs</div></div>
      <div class="glass stat"><div class="num"><%= stats.domainCount %></div><div class="label">Attack domains</div></div>
      <div class="glass stat"><div class="num"><%= stats.userCount %></div><div class="label">Registered hackers</div></div>
      <div class="glass stat"><div class="num"><%= stats.solveCount %></div><div class="label">Flags captured</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container" style="margin-top:1rem;">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="challenge-grid">
    <div class="glass panel">
      <h3 style="color:var(--fuchsia);">01 · Read the briefing</h3>
      <p>Every lab ships with a short scenario explaining what the target app does and what's broken in it — no guessing at the objective.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass panel">
      <h3 style="color:var(--cyan);">02 · Attack the live target</h3>
      <p>Each challenge opens as a real, running app in its own tab, fully isolated from every other lab. Interact with it exactly like a real pentest target.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass panel">
      <h3 style="color:var(--amber);">03 · Capture the flag, climb the board</h3>
      <p>Come back and submit the flag you extract to earn points instantly, track category progress on your dashboard, and see how you rank.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
